QuestData.Title: Meet with Gormok Ogrefist
QuestData.Description: Gormok Ogrefist sent an urgent message for you, $n. He wants you to join him immediately at The Barracks in Orgrimmar's Valley of Honor. He must have a mission of importance for you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Gormok Ogrefist at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Gormok Ogrefist at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
